    <summary><span data-ttu-id="a5c83-101">表示用于处理滚动菜单中重复按钮的可见性的数据绑定转换器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-101">Represents a data-binding converter to handle the visibility of repeat buttons in scrolling menus.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-102"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> 确定当菜单上的项目太多而无法在屏幕上显示时，菜单是否应显示重复按钮。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> determines whether a menu should display the repeat buttons when a menu has too many items to fit on the screen at once.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-103">使用带有四个绑定的 <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding> 的转换器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-103">Use the converter with a <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding> that has four bindings.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-104">这四个绑定应为父 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer>的属性：如果垂直组织菜单项（这是菜单的默认值），则绑定到 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedVerticalScrollBarVisibility%2A>、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.VerticalOffset%2A>、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentHeight%2A>和 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportHeight%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-104">The four bindings should be to properties of the parent <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer>:  If the menu items are organized vertically (which is the default for menus), bind to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedVerticalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.VerticalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentHeight%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportHeight%2A>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-105">如果菜单项是水平组织的，则绑定到 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedHorizontalScrollBarVisibility%2A>、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.HorizontalOffset%2A>、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentWidth%2A>和 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportWidth%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-105">If the menu items are organized horizontally, bind to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedHorizontalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.HorizontalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentWidth%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportWidth%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-106">将 <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding.ConverterParameter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 设置为0或100。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-106">Set <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding.ConverterParameter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to 0 or 100.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-107">该值被视为百分比，并确定当 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> 位于给定位置时是否隐藏某个按钮。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-107">The value is treated as a percentage and determines whether a button is hidden when the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the given location.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-108">当 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> 位于顶部时，<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> 的位置为0%，并且顶部按钮处于隐藏状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-108">When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the top, the position of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is 0% and the top button is hidden.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5c83-109">如果 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> 位于底部，则 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> 的位置为100%，底部按钮将隐藏。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5c83-109">When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the bottom, the position of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is 100% and the bottom button is hidden.</span></span>  
  
   
  
